485
00:18:23,894 --> 00:18:26,154
(all cheering)

486
00:18:26,230 --> 00:18:28,150
(grunting)

487
00:18:28,232 --> 00:18:30,942
That’s... my... son.

488
00:18:31,026 --> 00:18:33,986
(screeching)

489
00:18:34,071 --> 00:18:35,911
(yelling, grunting)

490
00:18:35,989 --> 00:18:36,909
Whoo-hoo!

491
00:18:36,990 --> 00:18:38,030
(sighs)

492
00:18:38,117 --> 00:18:39,577
(grunts)

493
00:18:39,660 --> 00:18:41,580
(groans)

494
00:18:41,662 --> 00:18:43,412
(grunts)

495
00:18:43,497 --> 00:18:44,497
(groans)

496
00:18:44,581 --> 00:18:45,871
Tap out!

497
00:18:45,958 --> 00:18:47,748
Don’t make me
break your arm!

498
00:18:47,835 --> 00:18:50,955
Lady, why don’t you break out
the lipstick and kiss my ass?

499
00:18:51,046 --> 00:18:52,336
There sure is a
lot o’ talkin’

500
