501
00:18:53,882 --> 00:18:55,762
Eh, that’s what you get
when you fight a woman.

502
00:18:55,843 --> 00:18:57,093
Yap, yap, yap.

503
00:18:57,177 --> 00:18:58,927
And they spend all day
eating bonbons

504
00:18:59,012 --> 00:19:00,392
and watching
<i>General Hospital.</i>

505
00:19:00,472 --> 00:19:03,022
Which, by the way,
has never been better.

506
00:19:03,100 --> 00:19:04,600
Mmm! Mmm!

507
00:19:04,685 --> 00:19:06,185
Okay, I give!
I give! I give!

508
00:19:06,270 --> 00:19:07,190
You’re better
than me!

509
00:19:07,271 --> 00:19:09,151
Really?
Ooh, thank you.

510
00:19:09,231 --> 00:19:10,271
Now, let me go...

511
00:19:10,357 --> 00:19:12,477
turn your back and take a bow.

512
00:19:12,568 --> 00:19:13,898
Okeydoke.

513
00:19:13,986 --> 00:19:14,896
(giggles)

514
